an> <span begin="00:09.057" end="00:09.573">dreamed</span> <span begin="00:09.573" end="00:09.699">of</span> <span begin="00:09.699" end="00:10.926">glory</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我年轻并梦想着荣耀时</span></p><p begin="00:11.365" end="00:13.004" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:11.365" end="00:11.597">You</span> <span begin="00:11.597" end="00:11.853">have</span> <span begin="00:11.853" end="00:12.202">no</span> <span begin="00:12.202" end="00:13.004">control</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你无法掌控</span></p><p begin="00:13.014" end="00:17.685" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:13.014" end="00:13.414">Who</span> <span begin="00:13.414" end="00:13.910">lives,</span> <span begin="00:13.910" end="00:14.214">who</span> <span begin="00:14.214" end="00:14.729">dies,</span> <span begin="00:14.729" end="00:15.065">who</span> <span begin="00:15.065" end="00:15.577">tells</span> <span begin="00:15.577" end="00:15.947">your</span> <span begin="00:15.947" end="00:17.685">story?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁能活着，谁会死去，谁来讲述你的故事？</span></p><p begin="00:16.745" end="00:18.012" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:16.745" end="00:17.302">President</span> <span begin="00:17.302" end="00:18.012">Jefferson</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">杰斐逊总统：</span></p><p begin="00:18.154" end="00:21.759" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:18.154" end="00:18.404">I'll</span> <span begin="00:18.404" end="00:18.570">give</span> <span begin="00:18.570" end="00:18.773">him</span> <span begin="00:18.773" end="00:19.368">this,</span> <span begin="00:19.368" end="00:19.659">his</span> <span begin="00:19.659" end="00:20.207">financial</span> <span begin="00:20.207" end="00:20.593">system</span> <span begin="00:20.593" end="00:20.706">is</span> <span begin="00:20.706" end="00:20.837">a</span> <span begin="00:20.837" end="00:21.045">work</span> <span begin="00:21.045" end="00:21.208">of</span> <span begin="00:21.208" end="00:21.759">genius</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“我得承认这一点，他的金融体系是一部天才之作”</span></p><p begin="00:21.788" end="00:23.607" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:21.788" end="00:22.020">I</span> <span begin="00:22.020" end="00:22.283">couldn't</span> <span begin="00:22.283" end="00:22.685">undo</span> <span begin="00:22.685" end="00:22.785">it</span> <span begin="00:22.785" end="00:23.002">if</span> <span begin="00:23.002" end="00:23.125">I</span> <span begin="00:23.125" end="00:23.607">tried</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“就算我想废除也无能为力”</span></p><p begin="00:24.494" end="00:25.677" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:24.494" end="00:24.854">And</span> <span begin="00:24.977" end="00:25.193">I've</span> <span begin="00:25.193" end="00:25.677">tried</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“而且我确实尝试过”</span></p><p begin="00:26.176" end="00:30.847" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:26.176" end="00:26.576">Who</span> <span begin="00:26.576" end="00:27.072">lives,</span> <span begin="00:27.072" end="00:27.376">who</span> <span begin="00:27.376" end="00:27.891">dies,</span> <span begin="00:27.891" end="00:28.227">who</span> <span begin="00:28.227" end="00:28.739">tells</span> <span begin="00:28.739" end="00:29.109">your</span> <span begin="00:29.109" end="00:30.847">story?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁能活着，谁会死去，谁来讲述你的故事？</span></p><p begin="00:29.857" end="00:30.997" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:29.857" end="00:30.406">President</span> <span begin="00:30.406" end="00:30.997">Madison</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">麦迪逊总统：</span></p><p begin="00:31.028" end="00:33.919" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:31.028" end="00:31.337">He</span> <span begin="00:31.337" end="00:31.522">took</span> <span begin="00:31.522" end="00:31.742">our</span> <span begin="00:31.742" end="00:32.125">country</span> <span begin="00:32.125" end="00:32.277">from</span> <span begin="00:32.277" end="00:32.979">bankruptcy</span> <span begin="00:32.979" end="00:33.134">to</span> <span begin="00:33.134" end="00:33.919">prosperity</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“他让我们的国家从破产走向繁荣”</span></p><p begin="00:34.347" end="00:35.277" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:34.347" end="00:34.526">I</span> <span begin="00:34.526" end="00:34.734">hate</span> <span begin="00:34.734" end="00:34.881">to</span> <span begin="00:34.881" end="00:35.132">admit</span> <span begin="00:35.132" end="00:35.277">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“虽然我讨厌承认”</span></p><p begin="00:35.687" end="00:38.818" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:35.687" end="00:35.901">But</span> <span begin="00:35.901" end="00:36.125">he</span> <span begin="00:36.125" end="00:36.395">doesn't</span> <span begin="00:36.395" end="00:36.560">get</span> <span begin="00:36.560" end="00:36.859">enough</span> <span begin="00:36.859" end="00:37.121">credit</span> <span begin="00:37.121" end="00:37.371">for</span> <span begin="00:37.371" end="00:37.609">all</span> <span begin="00:37.609" end="00:37.781">the</span> <span begin="00:37.781" end="00:38.114">credit</span> <span begin="00:38.114" end="00:38.329">he</span> <span begin="00:38.329" end="00:38.596">gave</span> <span begin="00:38.596" end="00:38.818">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“但他为我们建立的那些信用（贷款），并没有让他得到应有的赞誉”</span></p><p begin="00:39.300" end="00:43.928" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:39.300" end="00:39.657">Who</span> <span begin="00:39.657" end="00:40.153">lives,</span> <span begin="00:40.153" end="00:40.457">who</span> <span begin="00:40.457" end="00:40.972">dies,</span> <span begin="00:40.972" end="00:41.308">who</span> <span begin="00:41.308" end="00:41.820">tells</span> <span begin="00:41.820" end="00:42.190">your</span> <span begin="00:42.190" end="00:43.928">story?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁能活着，谁会死去，谁来讲述你的故事？</span></p><p begin="00:42.991" end="00:45.753" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:42.991" end="00:43.452">Every</span> <span begin="00:43.452" end="00:43.723">other</span> <span begin="00:43.723" end="00:44.215">founding</span> <span begin="00:44.215" end="00:44.587">father</span> <span begin="00:44.587" end="00:45.050">story</span> <span begin="00:45.050" end="00:45.266">gets</span> <span begin="00:45.266" end="00:45.753">told</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">其他每一位国父的故事都被传颂</span></p><p begin="00:46.164" end="00:48.936" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:46.164" end="00:46.591">Every</span> <span begin="00:46.591" end="00:47.007">other</span> <span begin="00:47.007" end="00:47.407">founding</span> <span begin="00:47.407" end="00:47.823">father</span> <span begin="00:47.823" end="00:48.138">gets</span> <span begin="00:48.138" end="00:48.306">to</span> <span begin="00:48.306" end="00:48.556">grow</span> <span begin="00:48.556" end="00:48.936">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">其他每一位国父都得以安享晚年</span></p><p begin="00:49.611" end="00:51.956" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:49.611" end="00:49.807">And</span> <span begin="00:49.807" end="00:49.980">when</span> <span begin="00:49.980" end="00:50.176">you're</span> <span begin="00:50.176" end="00:50.563">gone,</span> <span begin="00:50.563" end="00:50.783">who</span> <span begin="00:50.783" end="00:51.402">remembers</span> <span begin="00:51.402" end="00:51.586">your</span> <span begin="00:51.586" end="00:51.956">name?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当你离去，谁会记住你的名字？</span></p><p begin="00:52.043" end="00:57.175" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:52.043" end="00:52.443">Who</span> <span begin="00:52.443" end="00:52.909">keeps</span> <span begin="00:52.909" end="00:53.259">your</span> <span begin="00:53.259" end="00:53.709">flame?</span> <span begin="00:53.709" end="00:54.071">Who</span> <span begin="00:54.071" end="00:54.503">tells</span> <span begin="00:54.503" end="00:54.827">your</span> <span begin="00:54.827" end="00:56.501">story?</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:55.226" end="00:57.175"><span begin="00:55.226" end="00:55.594">(Who</span> <span begin="00:55.594" end="00:56.048">tells</span> <span begin="00:56.048" end="00:56.394">your</span> <span begin="00:56.394" end="00:57.175">story?)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁来讲述你的故事？</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁来守护你的火种？谁来讲述你的故事？</span></p><p begin="00:56.775" end="01:00.909" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="00:56.775" end="00:57.178">Who</span> <span begin="00:57.178" end="00:57.652">tells</span> <span begin="00:57.652" end="00:58.013">your</span> <span begin="00:58.013" end="00:59.027">sto</span><span begin="00:59.027" end="01:00.909">ry?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁来讲述你的故事？</span></p><p begin="01:01.830" end="01:07.333" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:03.815" end="01:04.075">I</span> <span begin="01:04.075" end="01:04.341">put</span> <span begin="01:04.341" end="01:04.932">myself</span> <span begin="01:04.932" end="01:05.157">back</span> <span begin="01:05.157" end="01:05.392">in</span> <span begin="01:05.392" end="01:05.675">the</span> <span begin="01:05.675" end="01:06.040">narra</span><span begin="01:06.040" end="01:07.333">tive</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:01.830" end="01:04.015"><span begin="01:01.830" end="01:04.015">(Eliza)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">伊莉莎</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我将自己重新放入这段叙事之中</span></p><p begin="01:08.368" end="01:11.896" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:09.365" end="01:09.579">I</span> <span begin="01:09.579" end="01:10.008">stop</span> <span begin="01:10.008" end="01:10.483">wasting</span> <span begin="01:10.483" end="01:10.926">time</span> <span begin="01:10.926" end="01:11.168">on</span> <span begin="01:11.168" end="01:11.896">tears</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:08.368" end="01:10.765"><span begin="01:08.368" end="01:10.765">(Eliza)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">伊莉莎</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不再把时间浪费在眼泪上</span></p><p begin="01:11.896" end="01:16.961" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:11.896" end="01:12.108">I</span> <span begin="01:12.108" end="01:12.366">live</span> <span begin="01:12.366" end="01:12.756">another</span> <span begin="01:12.756" end="01:13.513">fifty</span> <span begin="01:13.513" end="01:14.322">years,</span> <span begin="01:14.322" end="01:14.540">it's</span> <span begin="01:14.540" end="01:14.781">not</span> <span begin="01:14.781" end="01:15.516">enough</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:14.895" end="01:16.961"><span begin="01:14.895" end="01:16.961">(Eliza)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">伊莉莎</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我又活了五十年，但这还不够</span></p><p begin="01:15.861" end="01:20.375" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:15.861" end="01:16.190">I</span> <span begin="01:16.190" end="01:16.956">interview</span> <span begin="01:16.956" end="01:17.592">every</span> <span begin="01:17.592" end="01:18.226">soldier</span> <span begin="01:18.226" end="01:18.467">who</span> <span begin="01:18.467" end="01:18.865">fought</span> <span begin="01:18.865" end="01:19.086">by</span> <span begin="01:19.086" end="01:19.264">your</span> <span begin="01:19.264" end="01:20.375">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我采访了每一位曾并肩与你作战的士兵</span></p><p begin="01:19.523" end="01:22.812" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:19.523" end="01:20.018">She</span> <span begin="01:20.018" end="01:20.367">tells</span> <span begin="01:20.367" end="01:20.802">our</span> <span begin="01:20.802" e